3. DESIGN APPROACH
==================================================
This Listing Service may be implemented in one of two ways:
1. Fully live query service using integration clients to Car Service and User Service
2. Lightweight projection/read model persisted locally in PostgreSQL for faster listing queries

For this graduation project, implement a **simple defendable hybrid approach**:
- Listing table in PostgreSQL to store search-friendly car snapshots
- Integration clients to Car Service and User Service
- A sync/import service that can create/update listing projections from Car Service data
- Eligibility filtering in service layer

This makes the architecture easier to defend:
- Car Service remains source of truth
- Listing Service is optimized for search/read operations

